== Earlier Heaven Arrangement == In the {{ill|Fuxi Earlier Heaven Bagua|ja|伏羲先天八卦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, Zhen is the fourth in sequence and is positioned as one of the four corner trigrams, representing {{ill|northeast|ja|北東|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In terms of Yin-Yang transformation, it represents the emergence of one Yang.
